  <name>Egghead</name>
  <summary>Learn while having fun</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A simple trivia app to enjoy in your free time</p>
    <p>Below are the main features of Egghead:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download quiz</li>
      <li>Save downloaded quiz</li>
      <li>Delete saved quiz</li>
      <li>Switch to dark, light, or system mode</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="tld.vendor">
